{"tid":153164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"排隊落注嘈大交 馬會男遭扑頭爆缸","createTime":"2017-03-12T11:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T12:53:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc736407762125aaf8a5464b9caa642225b23038","tid":153164,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170312/large/1489312429_3b07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170312%2Flarge%2F1489312429_3b07.jpg&h=1f17951c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(簡明恩攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170312/large/1489312430_0e8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170312%2Flarge%2F1489312430_0e8e.jpg&h=d2685559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將軍澳寶林商場馬會發生傷人事案，一名男子遭人用告示牌擊傷頭部，現場遺下血迹。(簡明恩攝)<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳寶林商場馬會投注站，下午4時許，兩名男子疑因排隊問題爭執，其中一人拿起告示牌襲擊對方，事後逃去無蹤，職員見狀報案。警員接報到場，發現一名男子頭部受傷，召救護車將他送院治理，並於附近一帶兜截，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170312/56418287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170312%2F56418287&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR2zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d17a6b6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170312%2F56418287&h=9286b471\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170312/56418287</a>"},{"pid":"b9933b1b03282ce3739ee8303afe80628a284550","tid":153164,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"廢老輸唔切"},{"pid":"d8a87fd6cc182353c4f6b041d08562ac0e9256ba","tid":153164,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:23:26.000Z","msg":"頭獎"},{"pid":"c4529e5861b0b77f9828b5ebb79ffcf9c3e1